ke":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"我之前睇過一篇文章有完整地教點樣禪修，由初禪到更高嘅禪定 step by step咁解釋  不過我搵唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:51:34.000Z","msg":"好幾本都有，<br />\n藏傳：菩提道次第廣論<br />\n南傳：三十七道品<br />\n漢傳：瑜伽師地論、楞嚴經<br />\n等等等等。。。"},{"pid":"3a280c8168376869fcb30d036506c4f6fd58661b","tid":2346862,"uid":324681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唉～<br />\n點解要咁執著? <br />\n修行同環境同身份冇關。<br />\n <br />\n世界多煩擾，但你就係你，感官係客觀，但感受係個人。<br />\n<br />\n俾外界同自己生活模式影響係因為放唔低，放唔低，因為有執念，有期望，有顧慮。<br />\n<br />\n放唔低，就算一生一世天天上課但都只會一無所獲。"},{"pid":"daae40af1202db405035b351c47a16c31681fd0d","tid":2346862,"uid":318298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9984e4a07ae9a222e7f7b497cee04b7d72a36ab","tid":2346862,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a1b68686d516a2d3b7fd140ffc18139cd0d6e5f","tid":2346862,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea0be92bc001770cceeb977b4d37097f69e204c9","tid":2346862,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:19:54.000Z","msg":"巴打可否講多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:29:20.000Z","msg":"釋迦牟尼話講唔到<br />\n你叫我講多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:38:26.000Z","msg":"我意思係成件事情係咩事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:53:59.000Z","msg":"意會：從事、地、人、事、此時此刻，了解到道理。"},{"pid":"1cea3f92863e5ed9f0b8fec73814402917810ea4","tid":2346862,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:56:43.000Z","msg":"其實啲出家人去唔去到三摩地、初禪、二禪? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 