己嘅師父假死然後真死<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢啲知識/智慧應該要普及，愈多人知愈好，"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:22:02.000Z","msg":"巴打可否講解下止禪同內觀係咩，我自己對呢啲terms都好混亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sor ，我唔知內觀係咩&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n有好多人都知道喬達摩坐響菩提樹下，一直諗一直諗，唔飲唔食唔訓，諗到自己明白一切先會企起身。<br />\n<br />\n我無法確定呢個故事嘅真偽，但現代社會，大部份人都要養家供樓，我哋無辦法可以好似佢咁樣禪修，因為咁樣係唔現實，十分離地，舊時代嘅方法只適用於舊時代。<br />\n<br />\n作為現代人嘅你，除咗尋求禪修，亦要搵更多以外嘅野，例如哲學/心理學，人認識自己表和裏，其他人都認識你嘅表和裏，睇同一個人，但唔同人嘅評價會唔同，證明你唔可以只靠自己睇自己。所以要開放自己手腳，你覺得自己係好人？定你覺得人地覺得你係好人？<br />\n<br />\n思想會影響行為，但行為都會影響思想。<br />\n既然思想無法完全控制，我哋更應該控制自己嘅行為（做實質嘅善），先會影響自己嘅潛意識，進一步控制思想，反客為主"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T18:55:56.000Z","msg":"睇Existentialism睇到Existance Crisis <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而講潛意識首先比個Construct黎先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔同學派唔同學科對呢樣野有九千幾個Construct <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而輪迴論否定緊現實既一切 包括自己既Personal Identity同大眾認為Moral Responsibility都要重新定義 個人認為靜觀可以做 亦鼓勵做 但無必要相信背後果套宗教觀而西方一路都只係將呢套野抽走背後宗教元素叫人去做<br />\n(哲學上合唔合理就要自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"e039f418dd64425b8340ffb0b027820eae8e3bb9","tid":2346862,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ec713567d1978e07dc3ebcfb7ce1ebfebee2713","tid":2346862,"uid":286155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"daae40af1202db405035b351c47a16c31681fd0d","tid":2346862,"uid":318298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9984e4a07ae9a222e7f7b497cee04b7d72a36ab","tid":2346862,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:38:26.000Z","msg":"我意思係成件事情係咩事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:53:59.000Z","msg":"意會：從事、地、人、事、此時此刻，了解到道理。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T18:17:25.000Z","msg":"存在就係合理，就係答案<br />\ndon't think, feel"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T19:06:17.000Z","msg":"唔好將Hegel呢句野亂用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42189cb00af5e9aa4331879b1e81da32c11e121","tid":2346862,"uid":318298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e039f418dd64425b8340ffb0b027820eae8e3bb9","tid":2346862,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ec713567d1978e07dc3ebcfb7ce1ebfebee2713","tid":2346862,"uid":286155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"daae40af1202db405035b351c47a16c31681fd0d","tid":2346862,"uid":318298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:53:59.000Z","msg":"意會：從事、地、人、事、此時此刻，了解到道理。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T18:17:25.000Z","msg":"存在就係合理，就係答案<br />\ndon't think, feel"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T19:06:17.000Z","msg":"唔好將Hegel呢句野亂用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T00:01:35.000Z","msg":"Yes...而且這句說話，是很貼近生活經驗，但很很巨大的價值危機。"},{"pid":"7a8e0c1c0e0f51007f0c1e19224c718a5cbf1a8e","tid":2346862,"uid":318298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c42189cb00af5e9aa4331879b1e81da32c11e121","tid":2346862,"uid":318298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e039f418dd64425b8340ffb0b027820eae8e3bb9","tid":2346862,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ec713567d1978e07dc3ebcfb7ce1ebfebee2713","tid":2346862,"uid":286155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T18:17:25.000Z","msg":"存在就係合理，就係答案<br />\ndon't think, feel"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T19:06:17.000Z","msg":"唔好將Hegel呢句野亂用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T00:01:35.000Z","msg":"Yes...而且這句說話，是很貼近生活經驗，但很很巨大的價值危機。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T00:02:09.000Z","msg":"還有道德危機。"},{"pid":"8e5f0e5331f6ab4ea5b2755465a74be55dd3168b","tid":2346862,"uid":286155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7a8e0c1c0e0f51007f0c1e19224c718a5cbf1a8e","tid":2346862,"uid":318298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c42189cb00af5e9aa4331879b1e81da32c11e121","tid":2346862,"uid":318298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e039f418dd64425b8340ffb0b027820eae8e3bb9","tid":2346862,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T19:06:17.000Z","msg":"唔好將Hegel呢句野亂用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T00:01:35.000Z","msg":"Yes...而且這句說話，是很貼近生活經驗，但很很巨大的價值危機。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T00:02:09.000Z","msg":"還有道德危機。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T03:04:02.000Z","msg":"所以佛陀唔講<br />\n因為根本冇真理<br />\n千言萬語嘅解釋都比唔上真如"},{"pid":"2a07ef14470d671c542ed0962f5bb99554c8520d","tid":2346862,"uid":373794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b53edcf482552f8d5ce24ffb565996634aa1d2de","tid":2346862,"uid":286206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2d3a98d73d4279c279403348485aa8b767c24b0","tid":2346862,"uid":373794,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8fec64ec1a3199889fccb28c89a1990e23135c66","tid":2346862,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:22:02.000Z","msg":"巴打可否講解下止禪同內觀係咩，我自己對呢啲terms都好混亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sor ，我唔知內觀係咩&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n有好多人都知道喬達摩坐響菩提樹下，一直諗一直諗，唔飲唔食唔訓，諗到自己明白一切先會企起身。<br />\n<br />\n我無法確定呢個故事嘅真偽，但現代社會，大部份人都要養家供樓，我哋無辦法可以好似佢咁樣禪修，因為咁樣係唔現實，十分離地，舊時代嘅方法只適用於舊時代。<br />\n<br />\n作為現代人嘅你，除咗尋求禪修，亦要搵更多以外嘅野，例如哲學/心理學，人認識自己表和裏，其他人都認識你嘅表和裏，睇同一個人，但唔同人嘅評價會唔同，證明你唔可以只靠自己睇自己。所以要開放自己手腳，你覺得自己係好人？定你覺得人地覺得你係好人？<br />\n<br />\n思想會影響行為，但行為都會影響思想。<br />\n既然思想無法完全控制，我哋更應該控制自己嘅行為（做實質嘅善），先會影響自己嘅潛意識，進一步控制思想，反客為主"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T18:55:56.000Z","msg":"睇Existentialism睇到Existance Crisis <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而講潛意識首先比個Construct黎先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔同學派唔同學科對呢樣野有九千幾個Construct <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而輪迴論否定緊現實既一切 包括自己既Personal Identity同大眾認為Moral Responsibility都要重新定義 個人認為靜觀可以做 亦鼓勵做 但無必要相信背後果套宗教觀而西方一路都只係將呢套野抽走背後宗教元素叫人去做<br />\n(哲學上合唔合理就要自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T03:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實唔使咁複雜，只要接受佢套宗教觀，信有輪迴，d人就自然會覺得現世嘅無常，係十分平常（反正有下一世，下下世，下下下下&hellip;&hellip;世）<br />\n但同時有因果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，上世影響今世，今世影響死亡時嘅狀態，又會影響下世，如此類推<br />\n<br />\n宜家啲人對西藏宗教有幾種用途<br />\n<br />\n1.提升自我<br />\n無論係達到心境平靜，對生死嘅覺悟&hellip;&hellip;希望自己有所進步/改變<br />\n<br />\n2.尋找人生意義<br />\n基督教嘅人生意義就係要人為神而活，不再為自己而活；天主教嘅人生意義就係叫人因行為稱義，而得教死後升天家。<br />\n每個教派都有各自意義。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係因為電影/傳媒加深大眾對西藏宗教嘅認識，所以先愈嚟愈多人喺度尋求答案。<br />\n<br />\n3.學術研究<br />\n由20世紀到宜家，都仲有好多好多嘅學者想透過西藏宗教，搵一個新嘅視點研究佢個門學問"},{"pid":"c97768a692125ebfc19cb636dd02c06876c4d903","tid":2346862,"uid":7103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"913311bc362b915dad51be2c0d5be803adde1e54","tid":2346862,"uid":373794,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5b5eca37c24a1bd3e31f587cdf946e78ab3c0c5f","tid":2346862,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:18:39.000Z","msg":"冥想果陣個腦要諗啲咩？<br />\n定係放空就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"睇你想追求咩野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果想從煩忙生活中，偶而休息下，放空/臥床休息都達到放鬆心身嘅效果。<br />\n<br />\n如果想明白某啲道理，例如戒丁，就要不斷內觀，反問自己嘅心，點解會打丁，因為心理？定生理？<br />\n<br />\n如果想學識寬恕，就要自省，要諗下自己平時點樣對待人，做得好唔好？。<br />\n<br />\n因為冥想係一種全集中思考，類似「全集中呼吸」，用一種非常嘅思考模式睇事物，所以先會諗到野。<br />\n<br />\n你用全集中呼吸，一定要同時練劍先可以進步得快。<br />\n<br />\n你冥想放空嘅話，可能咩都諗唔到&hellip;&hellip;好似嘥咗啲時間，so unproductive&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T03:28:22.000Z","msg":"唔認同唔諗嘢=嘥時間=unproductive<br />\n<br />\n思緒/心靈有真正休息先可以真正提升效率"},{"pid":"466ebae482265799416300ee91fb8a84f7f39988","tid":2346862,"uid":373794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c97768a692125ebfc19cb636dd02c06876c4d903","tid":2346862,"uid":7103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"913311bc362b915dad51be2c0d5be803adde1e54","tid":2346862,"uid":373794,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5b5eca37c24a1bd3e31f587cdf946e78ab3c0c5f","tid":2346862,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:18:39.000Z","msg":"冥想果陣個腦要諗啲咩？<br />\n定係放空就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"睇你想追求咩野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果想從煩忙生活中，偶而休息下，放空/臥床休息都達到放鬆心身嘅效果。<br />\n<br />\n如果想明白某啲道理，例如戒丁，就要不斷內觀，反問自己嘅心，點解會打丁，因為心理？定生理？<br />\n<br />\n如果想學識寬恕，就要自省，要諗下自己平時點樣對待人，做得好唔好？。<br />\n<br />\n因為冥想係一種全集中思考，類似「全集中呼吸」，用一種非常嘅思考模式睇事物，所以先會諗到野。<br />\n<br />\n你用全集中呼吸，一定要同時練劍先可以進步得快。<br />\n<br />\n你冥想放空嘅話，可能咩都諗唔到&hellip;&hellip;好似嘥咗啲時間，so unproductive&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T03:28:22.000Z","msg":"唔認同唔諗嘢=嘥時間=unproductive<br />\n<br />\n思緒/心靈有真正休息先可以真正提升效率"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T03:29:49.000Z","msg":"如果追求心靈/思緒嘅休息，放空的確有效用。"},{"pid":"2f8fd9d31279c9e30ce553b421626fc319971257","tid":2346862,"uid":62482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:32:00.000Z","msg":"首先我認為要明白嘅係禪修並非為咗逃避或逃離現世<br />\n而係明白痛苦有其存在原因<br />\n深入體驗過後會從中超越痛苦, 得到解脫<br />\n好似上面有巴絲話過, 出面發生嘅事係客觀<br />\n但你嘅經歷係主觀, 加埋某程度上你認為出面發生緊嘅事只係你嘅投射, 係幻象<br />\n所以, 我理解係三摩地之後唔代表你一帆風順<br />\n反而係即使有「唔如意」嘅事, 你都唔再因此有煩惱<br />\n順着流走<br />\n<br />\n方法就我認為因人而異, 反正「條條大路通羅馬」<br />\n靜坐係有用的, 最簡單係留意呼吸, 慢慢感受就會更深, 有所感悟<br />\n「控制思想」呢樣嘢我唔建議, 因為係執著, 你有咁嘅諗法代表俾思想控制返轉頭<br />\n靜坐時有念頭好正常, 重點係你睇倒你有念頭浮出, 然後再留意返呼吸, 自然地會越去越深<br />\n當有啲經驗, 就能夠將呢種狀態融入日常生活<br />\n逐漸地意識會提高"},{"pid":"3da82ca929af25aa9d8ab1e371b163d4204a2b43","tid":2346862,"uid":62482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:33:57.000Z","msg":"最後, 祝大家新年快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6fb9fddcf15c62336dfc73b4d7d4c05def7067","tid":2346862,"uid":294423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"睇一行禪師d文章。<br />\n愈想要禪坐愈禪唔到，變成形式化。<br />\n禪係每天每步每事都可以禪。<br />\n簡單的專心步行，感受步行（感受腳板與地接觸，感受腳跟離地，感受身體筋鍵拉扯小腿同腳板）"},{"pid":"242157c60d33e33cec5e68aa1380431c4198966f","tid":2346862,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3da82ca929af25aa9d8ab1e371b163d4204a2b43","tid":2346862,"uid":62482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:33:57.000Z","msg":"最後, 祝大家新年快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:38:22.000Z","msg":"新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de16d685552d973d036f0ec361e035faeff4f69e","tid":2346862,"uid":123189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:25:49.000Z","msg":"睇莊子修埋道學會發現更多"},{"pid":"1a64e380c74883123a6f8b3f82b89eb25181458c","tid":2346862,"uid":88663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3a94b75987088e1dce70c3ece6d432983bd5f61c","tid":2346862,"uid":56639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f1df7fe7ff7c9363244e7d7e6f458f2fbf2b65b","tid":2346862,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c9c8bb8e5301328017721e750e0cc63f1c5e8f20","tid":2346862,"uid":56639,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:01:38.000Z","msg":"要靜落嚟冥想都已經好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:06:47.000Z","msg":"一合埋眼就好易諗其他野<br />\n呼吸又唔係好暢順<br />\n同埋想知係咪真係有好處"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5VDJGhwx6Lo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5VDJGhwx6Lo&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=42cde9a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5VDJGhwx6Lo</a><br />\n雖然靜觀並唔係禪修，但係我諗禪修嘅重點應該都係將注意力擺喺當下，放棄期望達到乜嘢境界，先會去到嗰個境界"},{"pid":"bd9e0234f9f2076488a6d1c3d4b9bb7f997dde6e","tid":2346862,"uid":73111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:49:24.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d1e455e7e53d5b66eb32e44ca9072e916f166994","tid":2346862,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a64e380c74883123a6f8b3f82b89eb25181458c","tid":2346862,"uid":88663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3a94b75987088e1dce70c3ece6d432983bd5f61c","tid":2346862,"uid":56639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f1df7fe7ff7c9363244e7d7e6f458f2fbf2b65b","tid":2346862,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:06:47.000Z","msg":"一合埋眼就好易諗其他野<br />\n呼吸又唔係好暢順<br />\n同埋想知係咪真係有好處"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5VDJGhwx6Lo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5VDJGhwx6Lo&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=42cde9a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5VDJGhwx6Lo</a><br />\n雖然靜觀並唔係禪修，但係我諗禪修嘅重點應該都係將注意力擺喺當下，放棄期望達到乜嘢境界，先會去到嗰個境界"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:50:31.000Z","msg":"我的確要let go呢個執著"},{"pid":"a010479f15727ff3f61ec17054d07dd332f02aac","tid":2346862,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1e455e7e53d5b66eb32e44ca9072e916f166994","tid":2346862,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a64e380c74883123a6f8b3f82b89eb25181458c","tid":2346862,"uid":88663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3a94b75987088e1dce70c3ece6d432983bd5f61c","tid":2346862,"uid":56639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:06:47.000Z","msg":"一合埋眼就好易諗其他野<br />\n呼吸又唔係好暢順<br />\n同埋想知係咪真係有好處"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5VDJGhwx6Lo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5VDJGhwx6Lo&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=42cde9a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5VDJGhwx6Lo</a><br />\n雖然靜觀並唔係禪修，但係我諗禪修嘅重點應該都係將注意力擺喺當下，放棄期望達到乜嘢境界，先會去到嗰個境界"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:50:31.000Z","msg":"我的確要let go呢個執著"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:59:26.000Z","msg":"有執着都係人之常情，覺察到自己有某種執着，咁咪借觀呼吸/步行/身體掃描/聆聽四周&hellip;&hellip;慢慢翻翻當下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔需要強迫自己唔執着"},{"pid":"281e78b4fec942dfe94a964ffe343a13a57e2a0e","tid":2346862,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T16:41:39.000Z","msg":"key word:清淨道論"},{"pid":"bd2d1d416e08213910d047285fb3f9fece046de9","tid":2346862,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"281e78b4fec942dfe94a964ffe343a13a57e2a0e","tid":2346862,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T16:41:39.000Z","msg":"key word:清淨道論"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T16:43:24.000Z","msg":"巴打好耐冇見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前上過個佛學post問問題不過已經冇人上 冇人答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"dcb128d42b2dc51f0d6a08a983d27d4b2d126f14","tid":2346862,"uid":54226,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"我之前睇過一篇文章有完整地教點樣禪修，由初禪到更高嘅禪定 step by step咁解釋  不過我搵唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}